ai-patthana16.5:0.2_0: (This should be expanded as in SN 4.)
ai-patthana16.5:0.3_0: And for the sake of nymphs, they’re committed to the worst kind of woven.
ai-patthana16.5:1.1_0: But causes and conditions don’t cause the reason for the sake of skillful teaching or for the sake of pride.
ai-patthana16.5:1.1_1: Then the skillful quality doesn’t cause or reason for the sake of success.
ai-patthana16.5:1.1_2: But they don’t cause any unskillful qualities to cause or reason for the sake of their lineage, nor for the sake of success.
ai-patthana16.5:4.1_0: No cause is skillful and unskillful.
ai-patthana16.5:4.1_1: No cause is the reason for breaking up and unjust means of the teaching.
ai-patthana16.5:4.1_2: No matter what is skillful and unskillful, they don’t arise because of cause or reason for the sake of hidden, or for the sake of both skillful and reasons.
ai-patthana16.5:5.1_0: Grounded by the unskillful and the three kinds of causes.
